’Ů@3af4e4c289ee15bc6a2a1990d420c7532cb28b4ca7fa383e7922ddfff33ca22fŮĽTitle: title: to tsv
Path: Flags
Content:
``--noheaders, -n``
: Do not output the column names as the first row.
``--columns {list<string>}``
: The names (in order) of the columns to use.
’Ů@70594f388d17a7daa1ee375c76db9217efa8a05f7466dbe29cf6a5572c271e42Ů`Title: title: to tsv
